<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN346">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>piṟa....................ḷa pāleṉa maṭuttali</l>
<l>ṉīṉṟa tāyō vēṇṭā ḷallaḷ</l>
<l>kalviye ṉeṉṉum vallāṇ ciṟāa</l>
<l>ṉolvē ṉalla ṉatuvā yākuta</l>
<l>laḻintō raḻiya voḻintō rokkaṟ</l>
<l>pēṇunarp peṟāatu viḷiyum</l>
<l>puṉṟalaip perumpāḻ ceyumiva ṇalaṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>…………………?</l>
<l>as for the mother who gave birth, she would not want [that].</l>
<l>The boy is a strong man who says “what of learning?”</l>
<l>I will not agree. That will become true.</l>
<l>When those that perish perish, [their] kinfolk are those that stay behind.</l>
<l>It will go to waste without obtaining those who cherish it,</l>
<l>the innocence of her who causes great ruin to [this] lowly place/[his] ruddy head.</l>
</lg>
